      "date": "2014-01-17 04:10:41.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: Verified-1\n\nAfter applying the patch on Lustre b2_5 branch, recovery-mds-scale test still failed with \"No space left on device\" failure:\n\n + dd bs=4k count=52579 status=noxfer if=/dev/zero of=/mnt/lustre/d0.dd-wtm-47vm5.rosso.whamcloud.com/dd-file\n dd: writing `/mnt/lustre/d0.dd-wtm-47vm5.rosso.whamcloud.com/dd-file': No space left on device\n\nMaloo report: https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/baa603f8-7f02-11e3-b6d1-52540035b04c",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
